text: is a town in Okhotsk Subprefecture, Hokkaido, Japan. As of May 1, 2017, the town had an estimated population of 5,029 and a population density of 18 persons per squared kilometre. The total area is 287.04 km². ==See also== * Hama-Koshimizu Station * Yamubetsu Station ==References== ==External links== *Official Website Category:Towns in Hokkaido
